PSCT.Tengu:
1 DARK Tuner + 1 non-Tuner Beast
① While this card is attacking, your opponent can't activate Spell/Trap Cards until the end of the Damage Step. 
② If an opponent's monster declares an attack: You can target that monster, then send 1 monster from your hand/field to the GY;
negate that attack.
